Besides, it doesn't happen on every date...<br>
<br>
Saph <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ualvimar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alvimar</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 134<br> <font color=#CC9900>(3/5/01 2:22:02 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Board Camping, we have been expert at it!!</span><hr size=1> Only person I've seen so far come out with an alternative was Adune but didn't see much support on it... I'll have to go digging to find it again unless he wants to post it. <p><FONT face="Comic Sans MS" size="2" font color=#8A2BE2>Bristlebane's best to you all,<br>
