21st season Enchanter</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukallikamerov.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kalli Kamerov</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Protector of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 400<br> <font color=#CC9900>(3/5/01 2:23:52 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://images.honesty.com/imagedata/h/895/90/28959015.jpg width = 135 height = 184></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Board Camping, we have been expert at it!!</span><hr size=1> Just every weekend raid for the past few weeks pretty much.  And considering that weekend raids are the only raids quite a few of the &quot;new&quot; 50's can attend, it just makes for an ugly board camping situation.<br>
<br>
