<br>
I have agreed with the 3 week thing for a long time.  We are a crowded server now and stretching that will also allow more people to sign up for Hate/Fear raids.  Each night when I log on, around 9pm CST, there are nearly 2400 people on the server at once.  I remember when servers where split when they had this many people on during prime time.<br>
<br>
I do think it's time that we address this problem though.  I don't think making rules that will disqualify someones raid would help.  We are trying to prevent FFA, not encourage it.  Let's make the changes so they benefit everyone, but also benefit the individual raid leaders as well.<br>
<br>
